EREC PRELIMINARY plan assessments from ENWAttached is the PRELIMINARY plan assessments from ENW for your business unit Note we have not included IT pass through items such as long distance market data WAN etc which is controllable at the business unit level and should be budgeted for by your business unit Please keep in mind this is PRELIMINARY and is subject to change The final plan assessments will be sent out September If you are not the correct person to receive these assessments or there is someone else that you would like to be included in this process please reply back to me with this information and I will add them to the contact list for future correspondence Thanks Kevin x
